rows.label: qst103910_msg0002
rows.name:
I transport goods between
Rigitte and Yeshiva Harbor.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0003
rows.name:
But if the cargo contains food,
the smell attracts them, and
they just swarm all over.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0004
rows.name:
You want to know the shipping
cost for the money being
sent to Iyasaki Village?

rows.label: qst103910_msg0005
rows.name:
The ship from Superbia arrives here
at Rigitte Harbor, and then...

rows.label: qst103910_msg0006
rows.name:
...the cargo is sent through the
Norem Cloudway to Yeshiva Harbor.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0007
rows.name:
It's prone to attacks by Cloud
Sea life, so I hire some
friends to act as guards.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0008
rows.name:
So... my cut is 2,500G, and
my friends get 1,700G each...
there are three of them...

rows.label: qst103910_msg0009
rows.name:
I receive 66,554G, so what arrives
for Correl-san will be 58,954G.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0010
rows.name:
It started at 90,000G?
Wow... that's quite a drop.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0011
rows.name:
If there were a direct route to Yeshiva
Harbor, there'd be fewer middlemen, so
it could be shipped much cheaper...

rows.label: qst103910_msg0012
rows.name:
Really? That would be wonderful!
Avaritian products are often high
quality, so that would be a huge help.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0013
rows.name:
However, we don't have
any long-distance Divine
Beast ships here, so...

rows.label: qst103910_msg0014
rows.name:
...it looks like we'll have to
ask the Avaritia Trade Guild.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0015
rows.name:
If you can make it happen,
everyone in Iyasaki Village
will be thrilled.

rows.label: qst103910_msg0101
rows.name:
This attack happened because
my client was being stingy...

rows.label: qst103910_msg0102
rows.name:
I couldn't pay my friends' wages,
so I tried to transport it alone...
and this is what happened.
